{Scorpina}

    The fem bot looked on as the battle raged around her, "By unicrons
shattered shell how the slag do I get myself into these things...?" Quickly
transforming the scorpion began dodging the cross fire looking for the best
place to sit this battle out, being new to the faction she didn't doubt
she'd be easily mistaken for an enemy so best to be scarce...
